### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health

###

### List all published posts (empty initially)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts

###

### Get post by slug (will 404 if not found)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts/my-first-post

###

### Login - get JWT token (run this first)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

> {%
client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token);
%}

###

### Create a post
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "My Second Post",
  "slug": "my-second-post",
  "content": "This is the full content of my first blog post.",
  "excerpt": "A short excerpt.",
  "status": "PUBLISHED"
}

###

### List posts again (should now show the created post)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts

###

### Get post by slug
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts/my-first-post

###

### Update post (replace 1 with actual post ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/posts/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "My First Post (Updated)",
  "slug": "my-first-post",
  "content": "Updated content.",
  "excerpt": "Updated excerpt.",
  "status": "PUBLISHED"
}

###

### Delete post (replace 1 with actual post ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### Attempt protected endpoint without token (should 401/403)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Should fail",
  "slug": "should-fail",
  "content": "No auth header."
}
